
a program that simulates a 2D canvas and draws various 2D shapes. 

The program draws in the following mode:

    F1: line mode
    F2: triangle mode
    F3: rectangle mode
    F4: circle mode

    f: toggles fill mode
    r: toggles drawing color red/black
    g: toggles drawing color green/black
    b: toggles drawing color blue/black
    c: clears screen
    q/Q/escape: quits program

Drag and release to get line
click and release 3 times to get a triangle
Drag and release to set two diagonal vertices of a rectangle
Drag and release to set the center and radius of a circle

